Swartswood is an unincorporated community located on the border of Hampton and Stillwater townships in Sussex County, in the U.S. state of New Jersey. Swartswood is  west-northwest of Newton. Swartswood has a post office with ZIP Code 07877.

* Gene Hill (1928–1997), writer
